description: Prime Development Opportunity in City Point.  This historic stand-alone single-family home, situated on a 2,500 sq ft lot, with a driveway accommodating 3 cars offers a rare opportunity for developers, builders & investors. The spacious residence includes an unfinished basement & attic, providing ample potential for expansion. Additionally, there is an opportunity to build up over the sunroom. The 1st floor features a large eat-in kitchen, living room, den & a year-round heated sunroom with direct access to the driveway & patio. The 2nd floor includes 4 bedrooms, a full bathroom & access to a large attic. The roof was installed in 2023.  Located just steps to Pleasure Bay Beach, Castle Island, MBTA, shops, restaurants & grocery stores. With close proximity to the Seaport & easy access to highways 93/90, this home is perfect for those looking to capitalize on renovation & expansion opportunities. Don't miss this unique chance to transform a historic gem into a modern masterpiece!
